TITLE: Defining a ScreenOrientation Plugin Interface in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript interface definition for a ScreenOrientation plugin that includes methods for getting, locking and unlocking screen orientation, as well as event listeners for orientation changes. The interface serves as a contract for platform-specific implementations.
