LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
interface Channel {
  id: string; // The channel identifier
  name: string; // Human-friendly name presented to the user
  description: string; // Description presented to the user
  sound: string; // File name relative to res/raw (Android), can be empty
  importance: Importance; // Level of interruption for notifications
  visibility: Visibility; // Lock screen visibility of notifications
  lights: boolean; // Show notification lights or not
  lightColor: string; // Light color for notifications, #RRGGBB or #RRGGBBAA
  vibration: boolean; // Whether notifications vibrate
}
```

