TITLE: Defining WriteFileOptions Interface in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Defines the options interface for writing a file using the Capacitor Filesystem API. Requires the `path` to write to, the `data` (string) to write, and the target `directory`. Optionally accepts an `encoding` (defaults to base64, use Encoding.UTF8 for string data) and a `recursive` flag (boolean, default false) to create parent directories if they don't exist.
