TITLE: Adding Event Listener for Orientation Change (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Enhances the ScreenOrientationWeb constructor to listen for native screen orientation changes and notifies Capacitor plugin listeners using notifyListeners. This allows external consumers to react to orientation changes consistently. It requires window.screen.orientation API support and the standard Capacitor event mechanism.
