TITLE: Registering ScreenOrientationPlugin in Java
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create the main ScreenOrientationPlugin class and register it with Capacitor. It includes method stubs for orientation, lock, and unlock functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v5/plugins/tutorial/implementing-for-android.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
package io.ionic.cap.plugin.plugins.ScreenOrientation;

import com.getcapacitor.Plugin;
import com.getcapacitor.PluginCall;
import com.getcapacitor.PluginMethod;
import com.getcapacitor.annotation.CapacitorPlugin;

@CapacitorPlugin(name = "ScreenOrientation")
public class ScreenOrientationPlugin extends Plugin {

   @PluginMethod()
   public void orientation(PluginCall call) {
       call.resolve();
   }

   @PluginMethod()
   public void lock(PluginCall call) {
       call.resolve();
   }

   @PluginMethod()
   public void unlock(PluginCall call) {
       call.resolve();
   }
}
```

