TITLE: Complete Podfile Configuration for iOS
DESCRIPTION: Full Podfile configuration including Capacitor pods and Firebase Messaging for iOS.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/docs/main/guides/push-notifications-firebase.md#2025-04-23_snippet_13

