```
 @PluginMethod()
 public void takePhoto(PluginCall call) {
   if (!hasRequiredPermissions()) {
+    requestAllPermissions(call, "cameraPermsCallback");
   } else {
     loadCamera(call);
   }
 }

 @PermissionCallback
 private void cameraPermsCallback(PluginCall call) {
   ...
 }

```

