TITLE: Updating ScreenOrientationPlugin for Orientation Detection
DESCRIPTION: This code updates the ScreenOrientationPlugin class to use the ScreenOrientation implementation for getting the current orientation type. It includes the load() method for initialization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v5/plugins/tutorial/implementing-for-android.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
package io.ionic.cap.plugins.ScreenOrientation;

import com.getcapacitor.JSObject;
/* Remaining imports omitted for brevity */

@CapacitorPlugin(name = "ScreenOrientation")
public class ScreenOrientationPlugin extends Plugin {

   private ScreenOrientation implementation;

   @Override
   public void load() {
       implementation = new ScreenOrientation(getActivity());
   }

   @PluginMethod()
   public void orientation(PluginCall call) {
       JSObject ret = new JSObject();
       String type = implementation.getCurrentOrientationType();
       ret.put("type", type);
       call.resolve(ret);
   }

   /* Remaining code omitted for brevity */
}
```

