TITLE: Implementing Lock and Unlock in ScreenOrientationPlugin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the implementation of lock and unlock methods in the ScreenOrientationPlugin class. It includes input validation for the lock method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v5/plugins/tutorial/implementing-for-android.md#2025-04-23_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
@PluginMethod()
public void lock(PluginCall call) {
   String orientationType = call.getString("orientation");
   if(orientationType == null) {
       call.reject("Input option 'orientation' must be provided.");
       return;
   }
   implementation.lock(orientationType);
   call.resolve();
}

@PluginMethod()
public void unlock(PluginCall call) {
   implementation.unlock();
   call.resolve();
}
```

