TITLE: Screen Orientation Lock Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the lock method that forces a specific screen orientation and updates the supported orientations mask.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v3/plugins/tutorial/implementing-for-ios.md#2025-04-23_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: swift
CODE:
```
public func lock(_ orientationType: String, completion: @escaping (UIInterfaceOrientationMask) -> Void) {
  DispatchQueue.main.async {
    let mask = self.fromOrientationTypeToMask(orientationType)
    let orientation = self.fromOrientationTypeToInt(orientationType)
    UIDevice.current.setValue(orientation, forKey: "orientation")
    UINavigationController.attemptRotationToDeviceOrientation()
    completion(mask)
  }
}
```

