TITLE: Converting Orientation Type to Android Activity Info Enum
DESCRIPTION: Helper method to convert JavaScript orientation types to corresponding Android ActivityInfo orientation constants.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v3/plugins/tutorial/implementing-for-android.md#2025-04-23_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
private int fromOrientationTypeToEnum(String orientationType) {
   switch (orientationType) {
       case "landscape-primary":
           return ActivityInfo.SCREEN_ORIENTATION_LANDSCAPE;
       case "landscape-secondary":
           return ActivityInfo.SCREEN_ORIENTATION_REVERSE_LANDSCAPE;
       case "portrait-secondary":
           return ActivityInfo.SCREEN_ORIENTATION_REVERSE_PORTRAIT;
       default:
           // Case: portrait-primary
           return ActivityInfo.SCREEN_ORIENTATION_PORTRAIT;
   }
}
```

