TITLE: Implementing Orientation Change Detection in ScreenOrientation
DESCRIPTION: This code adds methods to the ScreenOrientation class to track and detect orientation changes. It uses a nullable integer to store the previous configuration orientation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v5/plugins/tutorial/implementing-for-android.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
@Nullable private int configOrientation;

public boolean hasOrientationChanged(int orientation) {
    if (orientation == configOrientation) {
        return false;
    } else {
        this.configOrientation = orientation;
        return true;
    }
}
```

