TITLE: Defining StatOptions Interface for Filesystem Plugin - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Declares StatOptions, outlining the parameters to request metadata about a file using Filesystem.stat(). User must provide the path to the file (string) and the FilesystemDirectory under which to resolve this path. Inputs are utilized to locate and analyze the targeted file or folder. Depends on the FilesystemDirectory enum.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ionic-team/capacitor-docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v2/apis/filesystem.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
interface StatOptions {
  /** The path of the file to get data about */
  path: string;
  /** The FilesystemDirectory to get the file under */
  directory: FilesystemDirectory;
}
```

